This directory (firmware/core1/) contains the Core 1 UI and application firmware
for MokyaLora. This code has no source-level dependency on Meshtastic or any
GPL-licensed library. It communicates with Core 0 exclusively through the IPC
protocol defined in firmware/shared/ipc/, which is MIT-licensed.

